also i have another suggestion to add CNN benchmark in [pytorch/benchmark](https://github.com/pytorch/benchmark). inside intel we use [convnet-benchmark](https://github.com/mingfeima/convnet-benchmarks/tree/master/pytorch) to track the CNN performance.

